rComments: The class content is really enjoyable and will make you want to sit through the 3 hour lectures. Unfortunately, Rowen's midterm was 1.5 hours to write 2 essays, 3 1-2 page answers and 2 short answer questions. This did not give us enough time to apply what we learned. Also, the essay guidelines are not precise,resulting in confusion.
